The git-server can manage the git projects own use mysql database, It's easy.
  - use the mysql db can mange user SSH key.
  - Embedded into the web application.

=SETUP=
=======
  #  install pythonsetuptools
  $sudo apt-get install python-setuptools
  
  # download this git server version and execute
  $sudo python setup.py install
  
  # add git user
  $sudo adduser \
  $>–system \
  $>–shell /bin/sh \
  $>–gecos ‘git version control’ \
  $>–group \
  $>–disabled-password \
  $>–home /var/git \
  $>git
  
  # setting the git databse info
  $ vi /etc/git.conf
  
  # init the server
  $sudo -H -u git git-init < ~/.ssh/ids.pub
  
  # add database user data...
